Website Testing Command Plan (Bug Bounty Style) 🛡️
Phase 1 — Target Information Gathering (Recon)
1. Find Subdomains
subfinder -d target.com -all -o subdomains.txt

assetfinder target.com

amass enum -d target.com
2. Check Alive Domains
httpx -l subdomains.txt -o live.txt
3. Find IPs
dnsx -l subdomains.txt
4. Technology Detection
whatweb https://target.com

wappalyzer https://target.com
Phase 2 — URL Collection
5. Collect URLs
gau target.com

waybackurls target.com

katana -u https://target.com

Save:

gau target.com > urls.txt
6. Extract Parameters
cat urls.txt | grep "=" > params.txt
Phase 3 — Directory Bruteforce
7. Directory Scan
gobuster dir -u https://target.com -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirb/common.txt

Advanced:

feroxbuster -u https://target.com
Phase 4 — Port Scanning
8. Scan Ports
nmap -sC -sV target.com

Full scan:

nmap -p- target.com

Fast scan:

rustscan -a target.com
Phase 5 — Vulnerability Scanning
9. Nuclei Scan

(Most important tool)

nuclei -u https://target.com

Full templates:

nuclei -u https://target.com -t ~/nuclei-templates

Critical only:

nuclei -severity critical,high -u https://target.com
Phase 6 — JavaScript Analysis
10. Extract JS Files
katana -u https://target.com -jc

or:

gau target.com | grep .js
11. Secrets Finding
gf api-keys urls.txt

trufflehog filesystem .
Phase 7 — Parameter Testing
12. XSS Testing
dalfox file params.txt
13. SQL Injection
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" --batch
14. Open Redirect
gf redirect urls.txt
Phase 8 — Screenshot & Visual Testing
15. Screenshot Sites
gowitness file -f live.txt
Phase 9 — Takeover Check
16. Subdomain Takeover
subzy run --targets subdomains.txt
Phase 10 — Sensitive Files Check
17. Check Important Files
https://target.com/robots.txt

https://target.com/sitemap.xml

https://target.com/.env

https://target.com/admin

Automated:

dirsearch -u target.com
Phase 11 — HTTP Security Headers
18. Check Headers
curl -I https://target.com

or:

httpx -security-checks -u https://target.com
Phase 12 — Automation Workflow (Real Hacker Method)

Real workflow command chain:

subfinder -d target.com | httpx | nuclei

Advanced chain:

subfinder -d target.com | httpx | gau | nuclei

Pro workflow:

subfinder -d target.com -all | httpx | tee live.txt

gau target.com | tee urls.txt

cat urls.txt | gf xss | dalfox pipe

nuclei -l live.txt

